---
const faqItems = [
  {
    question: "Who runs the studio?",
    answer:
      "My name is Michael Andreuzza, UI Designer and Front end Developer. I also build products for myself.",
  },
  {
    question: "How do we communicate and manage the project?",
    answer:
      "studiomax uses Breeew for project management, ensuring seamless communication and collaboration.",
  },
  {
    question: "How quickly will I get some work done?",
    answer:
      "Expect the initial concept within 2-3 days, and studiomax will make revisions until it meets your complete satisfaction. For bigger projects, it can take up to 4 weeks.",
  },
  {
    question: "Why do you only have two spots?",
    answer:
      "studiomax believes in providing the best possible service to clients, and to ensure that, studiomax has decided to limit the workload to just two projects at a time. This approach allows studiomax to dedicate its full attention and expertise to each project, ensuring quality and timely delivery.",
  },
  {
    question: "What if I don't like the design?",
    answer:
      "studiomax wants you to be happy with the results! Hence the unlimited requests.",
  },
  {
    question: "Are there any refunds?",
    answer:
      "Unfortunately, not. Because of the intense creative demands for delivering top-notch design and development within tight timeframes and the thorough research invested to achieve the best outcomes, studiomax's cannot provide our services without compensation.<br /><br />However, we understand the importance of client satisfaction. If, after our initial discussion, it turns out that our services do not align with your needs and no work has been initiated, rest assured that you are eligible for a 100% refund. studiomax values transparency and wants our clients to feel confident in their interactions with studiomax's.",
  },
];
---

<section class="md:px-12 sm:px-8">
  <div class="border-x divide-y border-b divide-zinc-800 border-zinc-800">
    <div class="p-8 lg:p-10">
      <span class="text-white">‚è§ Frequent questions and answers</span>
      <h2
        class="text-5xl  tracking-wide text-balance md:text-6xl text-white mt-12">
        The answers to the most popular frequent questions
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-8 text-zinc-400">
        Can't find your answer? Send an <a
          class="text-sky-400 hover:text-white duration-200"
          href="mailto:michael@andreuzza.com"
          >email</a
        > and studiomax will get back to you.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-px bg-zinc-800">
      {
        faqItems.map((item) => (
          <details class=" bg-black">
            <summary class="w-full p-8 lg:px-10 text-left  tracking-wide cursor-pointer text-white focus:text-green-500">
              {item.question}
            </summary>
            <div class="text-sm text-zinc-400  px-8 pb-8 lg:px-10">
              {item.answer}
            </div>
          </details>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
